                            <comment id="16980298" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 22 Nov 2019 16:27:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1870172 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/issue45&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
